    "In this section, the datasets have been categorized and provide a comprehensive study of the image polyp datasets including CVC-Colon DB (Bernal et al. 2012), ETIS-Larib (Silva Kvasir-SEG CVC Clinic DB/ CVC Colon DB ETIS-LARIB DB Kvasir (Pogorelov et al. 2017) and Kvasir-SEG (Jha et al. 2020).",
    "All image polyp datasets are openly accessible.",
    "The CVC-Colon DB was the first dataset proposed for polyp segmentation.",
